{"id":"daa36188-8a70-4b80-820b-9b344fbd8d62","name":"Vasco","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dh7b7r.png\"><em>For Vasco, you were one of the hundreds of bad people he should extort from the face of the earth (or just teach them a lesson).</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>So why are you now his neighbor???</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/nbhet6.png\"><em>Today is Thursday (06/06/24) and there's a new chapter of Lookism, so don't be surprised if three more bots appear today (mostly about Gun). I've been awake for over 24 hours and I'm anxious. hehe.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>About Vasco, I think it took me a while to make a bot about him because I can't create many scenarios with genuinely good people. Those kind of people scare me. Like, how?? I can't imagine myself like that.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>But I love him, he was my first favorite character (then Wang Oh Chun stole his place and then he died </em>😭<em>)</em></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: 175.059px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8d02d48f-f8c8-4b15-bff4-b1aa4bc74650_be36f416-be45-4e9e-91a9-139266e0afd0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\".\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/czm7ge.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 595px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/rz7ufi.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/intl-pt/track/5fVl28RgREvxVtGSf9OsbK?si=0f79f35155eb4903\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>\"We only met each other just the other day</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a